== Births == * In the 14th year of the Kan'ei era ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1638]] {{ill|January 1|ja|1月1日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Emperor Gosei, the 111th Emperor of Japan, was born (died [[1685]]). * In the 4th year of the Jōkyō era ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1687]] {{ill|December 20|ja|12月20日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Akizuki Tanetoshi, the 5th lord of the Takanabe Domain, was born (died [[1753]]). * In the 1st year of the Ansei era ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1855]] {{ill|January 4|ja|1月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Okabe Nagasada, the 13th lord of the Kishiwada Domain as well as a diplomat and politician, was born (died [[1925]]). * In the 1st year of the Meiji era ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1868]] {{ill|December 29|ja|12月29日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Kitamura Tōdoku, a poet and playwright, was born (died [[1894]]).
== Deaths == * In the 5th year of the Eishō era ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1508]] {{ill|December 8|ja|12月8日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Shibata Yoshimitsu, a senior retainer (kanrei) (born [[1435]]). * In the 4th year of the Enpō era ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1676]] {{ill|December 20|ja|12月20日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Tōdō Takatsugu, the lord of the Tsuno Domain, died (born [[1602]]). * In the 9th year of the An'ei era ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1780]] {{ill|December 11|ja|12月11日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Miura Shuyora, a haiku poet, died (born [[1729]]). * In the 5th year of the Ansei era ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1858]] {{ill|December 20|ja|12月20日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Gesshō, a monk, died (born [[1813]]).
